Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.28,0:02:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am Zhào Zǐlóng of Changshan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.09,0:02:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A true tiger-like warrior.
