Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,General Zilong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.18,0:06:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,General Zilong has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My liege!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,General Zilong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Zhao!
