Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.60,0:40:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1043.182)}{\bord11}What man will determine victory or death?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.60,0:40:30.30,Song,,0,0,0,,{\k50}Xīng{\k50}wáng {\k53}shéi {\k45}rén {\k83}dìng {\k289}a{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.90,0:40:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1043.182)}{\bord11}Prosperity and decline have no cause, indeed!
